These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, ambient, indie, country
1. the fan of ambient is between the fan of indie and the fan of country##2
2. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of indie##1
3. the fan of classical is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | country | ambient | indie |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, fanta, water
1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking water is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | water | coffee | fanta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, rabbit, rat, snake
1. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the snake##2
3. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | hamster | snake | rat | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, banana, watermelon, cranberry
1. the person eating watermelon is between the person eating banana and the person eating plum##2
2. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
3. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food   | cranberry | banana | watermelon | plum |

